h1. app

h2. Purpose

Runs a Griffon application in standalone mode. This is an alias for [run-app|commandLine]

h2. Examples

{code:java}
griffon app
griffon test app
{code}

h2. Description

Usage: 
{code:java}
griffon [env]* app
{code}

Fired Events:

* @RunAppStart@ - When the app has been started
* @RunAppEnd@ - When the app has shutdown
